    COMPUNET TODAY :  5th MARCH 1990

 At last some good news on the local
access situation.

FASTRAK will be delivering the long
awaited equipment on Thursday morning.

As soon as we have it and get it set up
our tests will begin.

Although we wouldn't be silly enough to
make promises or predictions, it is
hoped we will be able to have full
working local access very very soon
after the initial tests. 

    Peter 
